title: Rich Boy: Growing Pains
description: Worthington Michael Sinclair, the Fifth, has succeeded in battling demons and the chains put upon him by his own family. Now he is facing a new situation as he tries to keep his new family together, and not fall into any of the traps being laid for him by others. Will he grow into his inheritance of money and power, or will he fall into one of the traps that others are only to happy to set for him?
author: Dan Kirk
